description: This is the condo in Andrew Square in South Boston that you've been waiting for! This condo is not only turnkey, but it has fantastic accessibility with highway access within 1 mile and less than a 5 minute walk to the Andrew T station! This first floor condo is all one level and made for easy living. The crown moldings and beautiful hardwood floors throughout feel luxurious and inviting. The open style living/kitchen area is great for entertaining! Granite countertops, newer appliances including a dishwasher, a brand new kitchen faucet and garbage disposal are all for your convenience.  You will find two spacious bedrooms with large closets along with a bathroom that has a jetted tub with a safety bar feature! Don't miss the in-unit laundry feature as well as a hidden access panel in the second bedroom! Easy show or visit the open house on Sunday, June 30th from 12-2PM. This is an opportunity not to be missed, so don't be shy!
